{"article_id":"hgeNMrAxZzcFGTMm","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Mary Ann Cavazos Beckett , Rick Jervis , Julie Garcia , Bart Jansen and Christal Hayes","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"SANTA FE , Texas -","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"A shotgun-toting teenager opened fire at a Texas high school Friday ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"killing at least 10 people","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"and leaving a cache of explosives in and around the area .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"Nine students and one adult were killed at Santa Fe High School in Santa Fe , Texas , amid gunfire","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"that erupted","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"before classes began ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"a law enforcement official","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"not authorized to comment publicly","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"told .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"The suspect was later taken into custody .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Ten other people were wounded ,","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Texas Gov . Greg Abbott said during an afternoon news conference .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"\" We come together today","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"as we deal with one of the most heinous attacks","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"that we ' ve ever seen in the history of Texas schools , ''","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"Abbott said .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"`` It ' s impossible to describe the magnitude of the evil of someone","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"who would attack innocent children in a school . ''","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"The attack once again heated up opinions about gun control laws and how to stop America 's gun violence .","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"The shooting was the worst since Feb. 14 ,","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"when a former student killed 17 people at a Florida high school","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"and caused polarized debate about gun control .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"The official said","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"multiple pipe-bomb-type explosives were recovered at the school ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"but investigators were still going through the building .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Authorities also found other explosives ,","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"including a CO2 device and a Molotov cocktail ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Abbott said .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Dimitrios Pagourtzis , 17 , was arrested after the shooting","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"and charged with capital murder and aggravated assault of a peace officer .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"After being read his rights ,","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"he admitted to the shootings","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"and told officers","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"he targeted students","depth":14},{"id":36,"text":"he did n't like ,","depth":14},{"id":37,"text":"according to a court filing .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"`` He did not shoot students","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"he did like","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"so he could have his story told , ''","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"an officer wrote in a probable cause affidavit","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"filed in Galveston County court .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"He made his first appearance in court Friday evening ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"hanging his head","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"and looking down","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"as a judge asked him routine questions ,","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"such as whether he wanted a court-appointed attorney .","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"`` Yes , sir , ''","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"he mumbled","depth":14},{"id":50,"text":"as he fiddled with his hands .","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"Pagourtzis kept a journal on his computer and a cell phone","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"that detailed the plans for his attack ,","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"Abbott said ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"adding","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Pagourtzis also hoped to take his own life after the shooting","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"but instead gave himself up to law enforcement .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"It ' s not ' s policy to identify minors","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"charged with crimes .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"Due to the magnitude of the event and the fact","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"the suspect could be charged as an adult ,","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"has decided to identify the suspect .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Pagourtzis was armed with a shotgun and a .38-caliber pistol ,","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"Abbott said .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"The guns were owned by the boy 's father ,","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"Abbott said .","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"Investigators were working on search warrants for two residences and a car ,","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"but were hampered by concerns about the potential for more explosives ,","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"Abbott said .","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"\" They want to make sure","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"they can enter them","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"without anybody being harmed , ''","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"Abbott said .","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"The school had two police officers on duty ,","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"and one was critically wounded in the shoot-out ,","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"according to Steven McGraw , director of the state Department of Public Safety .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"A state trooper also engaged the gunman ,","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"McGraw said .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"\" We know","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"that","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"because they were willing to run into that a building","depth":16},{"id":81,"text":"and engage them right now ,","depth":16},{"id":82,"text":"other lives were saved , ''","depth":15},{"id":83,"text":"McGraw said .","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"At least one other person was in custody ,","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"but the official believed","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"the person was not believed to be a suspect .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"After explosives were found at the school and off campus ,","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"police and the Santa Fe Independent School District urged people to report any suspicious items","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"found around town .","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"First responders received the first calls","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"about a gunman opening fire in a classroom at 7:32 a.m .","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"Witnesses","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"fleeing the school","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"described chaos","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"as they jumped over fences","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"and ran to nearby businesses .","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"`` I was shaking ,","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"my anxiety was bad , ''","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"Megan Hunter said","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"after fleeing her classroom .","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"`` I don ' t even know what to think . ''","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"The fire alarm went off during the attack ,","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"adding a level of confusion for those at the school and for first responders .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"It 's unclear whether a student , teacher or the gunman pulled it .","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"Some students told reporters","depth":14},{"id":106,"text":"that students pulled the alarm","depth":15},{"id":107,"text":"after seeing the gunman ,","depth":15},{"id":108,"text":"and one said","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"a former Marine","depth":16},{"id":110,"text":"who is a teacher at the school","depth":16},{"id":111,"text":"pulled the alarm .","depth":15},{"id":112,"text":"But Tyler Turner , a student at the school , told Fox News","depth":14},{"id":113,"text":"that the gunman pulled the alarm .","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"Turner said","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"a few of his friends walked past the gunman ,","depth":16},{"id":116,"text":"who looked suspicious .","depth":16},{"id":117,"text":"`` He pulled the fire alarm","depth":17},{"id":118,"text":"so we all went outside ,","depth":17},{"id":119,"text":"and then we heard 3 shots , ''","depth":16},{"id":120,"text":"Turner said .","depth":15},{"id":121,"text":"The suspect in the Florida high school shooting in February also was accused of pulling the fire alarm ,","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"allowing him to mow down students","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"fleeing the school .","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"For some students inside the school , the fire alarm made them think","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"the emergency was n't as dire .","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"Branden Auzston , an 11th grader at the school , heard the alarm","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"and thought","depth":14},{"id":128,"text":"it may have been a fire","depth":14},{"id":129,"text":"since they had a drill two weeks ago .","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"\" We go outside","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"and we were told to get in the grass , \"","depth":14},{"id":132,"text":"Auzston said .","depth":14},{"id":133,"text":"\" Then I see my teacher","depth":14},{"id":134,"text":"and she screamed","depth":15},{"id":135,"text":"' Just run ! ' \"","depth":15},{"id":136,"text":"He said","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"it felt like a movie","depth":15},{"id":138,"text":"and nothing seemed real .","depth":15},{"id":139,"text":"Eight hours after shots were fired inside his high school ,","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"Auzston and his girlfriend , Daisy Sullivan , gathered at the H-E-B parking lot across from what is being referred as the Alamo Gym ,","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"where parents and guardians are being reunited with students .","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"They hoped to find Auzston 's best friend , Chris Stone .","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"no one has talked to him since this morning .","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"`` I fell asleep earlier","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"because I didn ' t feel good ,","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"and I thought","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"I would wake up","depth":14},{"id":149,"text":"and it would be over","depth":15},{"id":150,"text":"and everything would be normal -","depth":15},{"id":151,"text":"but it ' s not , ''","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"Sullivan said ,","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"adding","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"in two weeks she 's scheduled to graduate .","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"Leila Butler , another student , told CNN","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"she didn ' t hear gunshots ,","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"but just the fire drill","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"that prompted the evacuation .","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"\" We ' re all really just devastated","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"that such a tragedy could happen in our small town , \"","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"she said .","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"Coupled with Hurricane Harvey at the start of the school year ,","depth":13},{"id":163,"text":"\" it ' s more than we can handle , \"","depth":13},{"id":164,"text":"she said .","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"TV aerial footage showed groups of students being herded out of the rear of the school","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"and a sheet","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"believed to be covering a body on the lawn outside .","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"Yellow buses stood at the ready","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"to shuttle students away .","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"President Trump called it a `` very sad day '' at the White House .","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"He spoke with Abbott","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"and pledged to work with the governor","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"to provide appropriate federal assistance .","depth":12},{"id":174,"text":"`` My administration is determined to do everything in our power","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"to protect our students ,","depth":14},{"id":176,"text":"secure our schools","depth":15},{"id":177,"text":"and to keep weapons out of the hands of those","depth":16},{"id":178,"text":"who pose a threat to themselves and to others , ''","depth":16},{"id":179,"text":"Trump said .","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"`` May God heal the injured","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"and may God comfort the wounded . ''","depth":12},{"id":182,"text":"Later Friday evening , hundreds of locals crowded into a grassy lot next to Texas First Bank for a vigil","depth":9},{"id":183,"text":"honoring the slain and injured .","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"Some cried","depth":11},{"id":185,"text":"and hugged ,","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"others held roses or white candles .","depth":10},{"id":187,"text":"Many were students","depth":10},{"id":188,"text":"who , just hours earlier , had hid under desks or flung themselves over fences","depth":11},{"id":189,"text":"to flee the gunman .","depth":11},{"id":190,"text":"A table held 10 candles , 10 white roses and 10 bibles for the 10 victims .","depth":8},{"id":191,"text":"\" Words can not express the sorrow of our hearts for those","depth":10},{"id":192,"text":"we have lost , \"","depth":10},{"id":193,"text":"said Leigh Wall , superintendent of Santa Fe ISD .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":387,"left":0,"right":386,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":386,"left":1,"right":385,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":385,"left":215,"right":384,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":215,"left":211,"right":214,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":211,"left":205,"right":210,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":205,"left":196,"right":204,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":2,"right":195,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":204,"left":201,"right":203,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":198,"right":200,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":5,"right":197,"relation":"elaboration","nuclear